<br>
When to use this pet?  High DPS group with low healing.  Got a SK, ROG, ENC, MAG, DRU, RNG group like I did today?  63 fire pet says the DRU plays like a full cleric with the reduced mob DPS.  (The air doesn't stun as much.  Fire's lower HP doesn't matter since it's not getting agro and you already have plenty of DPS.)<br>
<br>
Let's not bicker and argue over who killed who.  The fire pets are situational but there are situations where they are very effective.<br>
<br>
  One mage's opinion,<br>
